headline: UDR, Inc., original pioneers of multifamily centralization, partner with Funnel to complete operations revolution across nearly 60,000 units
summary: Funnel, the proven AI-infused multifamily CRM, today announced its newest partner UDR, Inc., (NYSE: UDR) NMHC's 14th-largest multifamily owner-operator in the United States and long-standing leader in multifamily centralization.
